title: Gary Kinder - Ship of Gold in the Deep Blue Sea (rip-oop)
description:
Ship of the Deep Blue Sea
By Gary Kinder, 1998
Narrated by Bruce Davinson, Random House, 1998
4 cassettes, 4h49m, Abridged
Recorded to MP3 with with Total Recorder @ 128 kbits/sec, 44 100 Hz on March 2014

A true adventure story of salvaging gold from an old ship. It's something of a classic. The only audio available is abridged, but not terribly so. The tapes I bought were still in shrinkwrap, this is the first playing ever.
